
= Mailing lists =
There are many mailing lists in the oVirt project - mostly referenced on [http://lists.ovirt.org/mailman the oVirt mailman page]. This page describes the main lists and their scope.

== User-oriented lists ==
* [http://lists.ovirt.org/mailman/listinfo/announce Announce]: Announcements about the oVirt project
* [http://lists.ovirt.org/mailman/listinfo/users Users]: The best place for oVirt user issues - installation, configuration, storage integration, use-cases

== Developer-oriented list ==
* [http://lists.ovirt.org/mailman/listinfo/devel Devel]: Project-wide developer-related issues. Anything which requires the feedback or awareness of developers within the oVirt project should go here.

== Project governance and management ==
* [http://lists.ovirt.org/mailman/listinfo/board Board]: Discussions amongst the Board for all business
* [http://lists.ovirt.org/mailman/listinfo/infra Infra]: List for oVirt.org Infrastructure team
* [http://lists.ovirt.org/mailman/listinfo/marketing Marketing]: List for the oVirt marketing working group
* [http://lists.ovirt.org/mailman/listinfo/wiki Wiki]: help for writers and editors of the oVirt wiki

